values: I can't believe I joined so many themed writing communities. X__x Oh well, I did say that I wanted to practice my writing and since I usually need inspiration to get things going, this is the best way to practice. Pairings to write: ZabuHaku for (Almost half done with this! Go me!) KisaIta for (This is going to be *so* fun...::evil cackle::) S/C for I just joined because I wanted to write SeiSub. :P And haha, I just realized that the themed communities that appeal to me are the dark and angsty ones. Oh dear...^^ I also want to try out the "Breaking Point" theme for and the Rain theme for . I have the general plot in mind but lately either I've been too busy or...I've been too lazy to write. :P
First entry, whoo! This is my writing journal, and any fics, drabbles, and other inventions of my crazy mind will go here. O__o
